  </div>

  <div class='about_section e'>
    <h3 id=contact> Contact </h3>
    <p> We are headquartered in <b>Tel Aviv</b>, Jabotisnky Rd 41, suite 2. </p>
    <p>
      <p>+972-3-8244450 / +972-52-293-4321</p>
      <p>Email us at <a mailto=hi@good-weed.co>hi@good-weed.co</a> or <a onclick=contact()>click here</a> to leave your email and we'll be in touch.</p>
